Text: Thanks for this upload.  Did my FLAC upload of Through Being Cool yesterday inspire you? :)
Hah! It did actually, I was amazed that I found Through Being Cool FLAC, and thought other people would feel the same about this album. It was actually my first torrent, too.

That's why I upload obscure stuff that I love from the 90's.  There are almost no torrents in FLAC for the bands I like so I make my own.  I lost my copy of Stay What You Are so your upload made my day.
